[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "（システム）",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "一か月後――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_720_038_00835",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 965274698
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "お困りの方はいませんか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00836",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ご入用のものはございませんか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00837",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "皆さんのそのお悩みごと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00838",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "錬金術士レスナにお任せあれ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00839",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "錬金術でなんでも解決します！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00840",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "住民Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "レスナさん、こんにちは！\nこの間お願いした、薬なんですが……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_547_038_00841",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "はい！　ご用意できています！\n用法のメモを添えているので、読んでくださいね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00842",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "住民Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ありがとうございます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_547_038_00843",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "住民Ｂ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あの、子どもに持たせる護身用の道具とか、\n用意してもらえませんか……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_548_038_00844",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "もちろんです！　お子様に持たせても安心な\n道具をご用意できますよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00845",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（果ての大陸から戻ってきた後も、\n　私は変わらず錬金術士として活動しています）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00846",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（でも、前と確実に変わったのは――）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00847",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "住民Ｂ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あ、ありがとうございます！\n錬金術士レスナさんに相談してよかった……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_548_038_00848",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（錬金術が、多くの人に受け入れられたということ）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00849",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（そして、錬金術で多くの人の生活を豊かにする\n　お手伝いができているということ！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00850",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "あ、レスナちゃんいた！\n殿下とブラッドさんがお呼びだよー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00851",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "イザナちゃん！　そのお二人ということは、\nきっとお仕事の話だね。今から行くよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00852",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "レスナちゃん、忙しくて疲れちゃってない？\n空き時間も、たくさんの人の相談に乗ってるんでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00853",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん。でも、疲れを忘れちゃうくらい楽しいんだ。\n錬金術の力で、たくさんの人を助けることができて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00854",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "マナ資源に困らなくなって、大規模な錬金術とか、\n国からのお仕事とか、張り切っちゃって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00855",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "錬金術士として名前が知られて責任も増えたけど、\n私は今の状況にすごくやりがいを感じてるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00856",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（あれから私は、ロマンさんやブラッドさんと共に\n　錬金術を用いた国家事業計画に携わっています）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00857",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ブラッドさんたちが秘密裏に動いていたらしく、\n　とんとん拍子に計画は進んでいて――）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00858",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（手始めに、暗黒の氷海の門を参考にして\n　ルイネ州の「閉ざさずの門」を修復……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_042_01507",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（それによって黄金星からのマナの運搬が容易になり、\n　計画の進行に大きく貢献しました）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_042_01508",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（錬金術の力の下、\n　ランターナはどんどん発展していきそうです）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00859",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ヴァレリアも、錬金術士として国に協力しつつ、\n　九偉人と共に魔物退治とかで各地を回っていて――）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00860",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（アルビーナは諸島同盟の錬金術士代表として、\n　案内人の仕事をしつつ、島々を巡っているみたい）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00861",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（みんな忙しいけれど、それも錬金術が復興したからと\n　考えると、嬉しい忙しさです）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00862",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（そして、さらに私は――）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00863",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（錬金術士の教育や免許に関する体系の構築も\n　お手伝いさせてもらっています）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00864",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（あれから、ランターナでも無数島群域でも、\n　錬金術士になりたいという方がたくさん現れました）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00865",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私は、そんな方々に錬金術を教えています。\n　錬金術を、正しく使えるように）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00866",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（それが、立派な錬金術士としての責任。\n　これからの私がやらなくちゃいけないこと）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00867",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（果ての大陸を見つけることは終着点なんかじゃない。\n　むしろ始まりなんだ）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00868",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "やっほー、二人とも！\n私たちもご一緒していいかしら？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00869",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "美少女錬金術士のアルビちゃんもいるよーん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00870",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヴァレリア！　アルビーナ！\nもしかして二人も？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00871",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ええ！　錬金術士として力を貸してくれって、\nロマンたちからオシゴトの依頼よ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00872",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "アタシは錬金術士半分、案内人半分ってとこかなー。\n二足の草鞋、かっちょいいっしょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00873",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "今回はどんなオシゴトかしら。\nま、レスナとアルビーナと一緒だし、なんでも楽勝ね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00874",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、そうだね！\n力を合わせて一緒に頑張ろう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00875",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "おーう！　頑張ろー！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00876",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "再び、始まりそうです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00833",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "錬金術の時代が……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00834",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]